      • onComplete

        void onComplete(Bundle values)
        Called when a dialog completes.

        This method will always be called on the UI Thread

        Parameters:
        values - Key-value string pairs extracted from the response.

      • onCancel

        void onCancel()
        Called when a dialog is canceled by the user.

        This method will always be called on the UI Thread

      • onException

        void onException(Exception exception)
        Called when an exception is thrown during the authentication process. The following exceptions may be raised :
        DeezerError
        occurs if Deezer services refuse the request for any reason (including authentication). It might be because of invalid request parameters, or missing Permissions.
        DialogError
        encapsulate errors triggered by the authentication webview.

        This method will always be called on the UI Thread

        Parameters:
        exception - the exception that was raised
